  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to see whether systemic corticosteroids (such as
      Prednisone) have an effect on the peripheral blood Treg and Th17 function in patients with
      CRS. Patients are taking prednisone as part of their routine medical care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
